&lt;p&gt;Design and maintain system workflows for plan changes, exceptions, and adjustments&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop and execute testing strategies to validate system accuracy before each compensation cycle&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Provide technical guidance during plan design discussions, advising on system capabilities and constraints&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
