&lt;h3 class=&quot;heading&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Integration &amp;amp; Architecture&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build and maintain integrations between the ICM platform and source systems (CRM, ERP, HRIS, billing platforms)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ensure data integrity across the compensation data pipeline, from opportunity data through final payout&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner with Data Engineering and Revenue Operations to define data requirements and resolve data quality issues&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Document data flows, transformation logic, and system dependencies&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;heading&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;System Administration &amp;amp; Optimization&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Serve as the primary system administrator for the ICM platform, managing user access, security, and system health&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Identify opportunities to streamline and automate compensation processes, reducing manual intervention and cycle time&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Monitor system performance and troubleshoot calculation errors or integration failures&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Evaluate and recommend new technologies, including Claude-powered solutions, to enhance system capabilities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;heading&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reporting &amp;amp; Analytics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build and maintain reporting infrastructure within the ICM platform to support compensation dashboards and attainment tracking&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner with Revenue Operations and Accounting to deliver accurate, timely compensation data for forecasting and accruals&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enable self-service reporting for compensation administrators and business partners&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;heading&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You may be a good fit if you have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A passion for Anthropic&#39;s mission to build safe, transformative AI systems&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5+ years of experience implementing or administering ICM platforms (e.g., Xactly, Varicent, Anaplan)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong technical skills with experience in SQL, data integration tools, and system configuration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proven ability to translate business requirements into system logic and maintain accurate, auditable calculations&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience managing data pipelines and ensuring data quality across integrated systems&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong problem solving skills with a systematic approach to debugging and root cause analysis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Excellent documentation practices and ability to communicate technical concepts to non-technical stakeholders&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in a technical or quantitative field preferred&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;heading&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strong candidates may also have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience with full ICM platform implementation projects, including vendor selection and data migration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proficiency with APIs and integration platforms (e.g., Workato, Fivetran, custom ETL)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience with Salesforce administration or development&lt;/p&gt;
